ourth in the main race after starting on pole.\", \"from\": 7857, \"to\": 8079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a difficult weekend\", \"from\": 7869, \"to\": 7888}, {\"ngram\": \"Verstappen\", \"from\": 7893, \"to\": 7903}, {\"ngram\": \"17th\", \"from\": 7918, \"to\": 7922}, {\"ngram\": \"the sprint\", \"from\": 7926, \"to\": 7936}, {\"ngram\": \"his first pointless finish\", \"from\": 7940, \"to\": 7966}, {\"ngram\": \"any race format\", \"from\": 7970, \"to\": 7985}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2016 Belgian Grand Prix\", \"from\": 7992, \"to\": 8019}, {\"ngram\": \"the main race\", \"from\": 8042, \"to\": 8055}, {\"ngram\": \"pole\", \"from\": 8074, \"to\": 8078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Horner exit There were rumblings across the paddock in the first half of the season that all was not well at Red Bull and had not been since the storm in 2024 when a female team employee had accused principal Christian Horner of sexual misconduct.\", \"from\": 8081, \"to\": 8329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8291, \"end\": 8307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Horner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Christian Horner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Horner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Horner\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rumblings\", \"from\": 8104, \"to\": 8113}, {\"ngram\": \"the paddock\", \"from\": 8121, \"to\": 8132}, {\"ngram\": \"the first half\", \"from\": 8136, \"to\": 8150}, {\"ngram\": \"the season\", \"from\": 8154, \"to\": 8164}, {\"ngram\": \"Red Bull\", \"from\": 8190, \"to\": 8198}, {\"ngram\": \"the storm\", \"from\": 8222, \"to\": 8231}, {\"ngram\": \"a female team employee\", \"from\": 8245, \"to\": 8267}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual misconduct\", \"from\": 8310, \"to\": 8327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the beginning of July, Verstappen's car was struggling to keep pace with the McLarens, which led to whispers that Mercedes were